text: numba apa veta pæminimata pera da numba apa veta pæminimata pasu da api pidavata pat karanu læbuvemu yæyi ovuhu pævasuvoya. numbalage paramadhipati numbalage saturan vinasa kara dama numbala va polove niyojanaya karannata salasvannata puluvana. evita numbala kriya karanuye kese dæyi ohu avadhanayen balanu ætæyi ohu pævasiya
